{"tid":1146853,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[巫師?仁王?一款手辦兩個角色]【浪人傑洛特手辦公開】","createTime":"2019-05-09T13:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T07:36:57.000Z","uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bb56c06731fd4b1f92543f746dccb4685a1e24f8","tid":1146853,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T13:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VFrFQG3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVFrFQG3.jpg&h=86f46164&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCDPR新開的在線商城上架了一款浪人造型的傑洛特手辦，CDPR的相關人員表示他們對日本充滿熱愛，也經常聽到傑洛特的故事和妖怪文化有共通性的說法。<br />\n<br />\n手辦的設計靈感源於Okunoin Cemetery，背後的貓頭鷹是一只叫「崇妖」的妖怪。未來還會有日式風格的希里推出。 ​​​​<br />\n<br />\n預購頁面：<br />\n<a href=\"https://eu.store.cdprojektred.com/product-eng-38-Geralt-Ronin-Figure.html?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feu.store.cdprojektred.com%2Fproduct-eng-38-Geralt-Ronin-Figure.html%3F&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYZKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=50b2793e\" target=\"_blank\">https://eu.store.cdprojektred.com/product-eng-38-Geralt-Ronin-Figure.html?</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F7nqhnj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF7nqhnj.jpg&h=7fba730c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XPWKxVE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXPWKxVE.jpg&h=70474a33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eCBB8t0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeCBB8t0.jpg&h=5c5d22d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KEW232k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKEW232k.jpg&h=cdfa76a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xPqSGO1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxPqSGO1.jpg&h=ef9bdb88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wGwOe81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k